## Standard section order — NEW invoices (match Margarita)

1. Program / curriculum overview  
2. **Program Investment** heading  
3. **Orange performance guarantee banner** — only when CJ says guarantee yes  
4. **Terms agreement gate**  
5. **Locked** investment box: in-house checkout + Splitit helper (if CJ wants Splitit) + third-party financing (only what CJ names)  
6. **Next Steps After Payment**  
7. **Welcome to the HTSA Family**  
8. Reviews / testimonials / footer  

Do **not** duplicate the Terms clarification band after Welcome—reviews/footer follow Welcome.

