## Terms gate — REQUIRED content & copy (Margarita-aligned)

Duplicate structure from **`htsa-enrollment-margarita-de-la-rosa.html`**, then localize `data-*` only on the **new** file:

- **PDF:** [`https://closewithcjclay.com/HTSA-Terms-of-Service.pdf`](https://closewithcjclay.com/HTSA-Terms-of-Service.pdf) — visible label per Margarita (**“View Full Terms of Service (PDF)”** anchor class **`hts-terms-agreement-pdf`**).
- **Clarifications** inside the gate (same substantive blocks Margarita uses): Lifetime access; **1-on-1 coaching**; **AI role-play platform** clarification list items.
- **Checkbox:** *I have read and agree to the Terms of Service linked above.*
- **Button:** *Record agreement & unlock payments*
- Buttons below stay visually disabled / intercepted until **`recordTermsAgreement`** posts successfully; **`sessionStorage`** key unlock persists for session.
- **Never** paste the **CJ practice** simulated-payment UI onto real client invoices.

