## Payload — `recordTermsAgreement` (must include)

JSON fields sent via URL-encoded **`payload=`** POST (see Margarita `/` practice implementations):

| Field | Source |
|--------|--------|
| `action` | `recordTermsAgreement` |
| `fullName` | `data-full-name` |
| `email` | `data-email` |
| `phone` | `data-phone` (E.164-style string matching billing `tel:` — e.g. `+17081234567`) |
| `enrollmentPageUrl` | `window.location` canonical (path + optional query — no `#` hash noise) |
| `clientSlug` | `data-client-slug` (lowercase hyphenated slug) |
| `termsUrl` | `https://closewithcjclay.com/HTSA-Terms-of-Service.pdf` |
| `termsVersion` | `HTSA-TOS-PDF-closewithcjclay-2026-04` |
| `userAgent` | Client browser string |

Keep **`hts-enrollment-webapp-google-apps-script-sample.gs`** semantics aligned—the sample already logs **phone**.

