## 1. Legacy / sent invoices are FROZEN

- Do **not** refactor or “bring up to date” old pages unless **CJ names one exact filepath** for that client.
- Margarita remains the **timeline anchor** (**first Terms-gate invoice**)—do not rewrite Margarita unless CJ deliberately requests it.

