## 2. “Guarantee yes/no” = orange banner ONLY — not Terms gate

When CJ answers **orange performance guarantee yes/no**:

- **`yes`** → include **`enrollment-guarantee-banner`** directly under the **Program Investment** heading and above the **Terms agreement gate** (copy wording from frozen gold references — **never** edit legacy files in place — **read**/copy blocks only).
- **`no`** → **omit** the orange banner.
- Terms gate remains **mandatory** on NEW invoices regardless of orange answer.

## 3. Payment setup — CJ’s words only

| CJ says | You include |
|---------|--------------|
| In-house cash **only** | Whop **PIF** + **Splitit** explanation (optional if CJ asks) + **4-pay** blocks **without** external pre-qual links |
| In-house **+ financing** | All in-house tiers CJ wants **plus financing** tiles **only by name** (**ClarityPay / PayVa / Flexxbuy** combinations CJ explicitly specifies) |

**Never** invent unseen financing vendors.

