## 4. NEW invoice workflow + delivery checklist

1. `cp htsa-enrollment-margarita-de-la-rosa.html → htsa-enrollment-{slug}.html`.  
2. Replace client fields (`<title>`, hero, billing, steps, Welcome, **`data-*`**, **`STORAGE_KEY`**, JS slug fallback).  
3. Adjust investment HTML **only inside the new copy** — no legacy edits.  
4. **`grep`** — zero phantom names/contacts left from template duplication.  
5. Verify lock **before** record; unlock **after** successful post.  
6. **`git add`** **only** the new HTML (and optionally this `.mdc`/`.cursor/skills` when edited in **same chore** — never stage review PDF/HTML scratch files).  
7. Commit + push.  
8. Return **exactly**:

   `https://closewithcjclay.com/htsa-enrollment-{slug}.html`

   **Never** paste `?v=` cache-busting parameters unless **CJ explicitly requests** busting CDN/browser cache.

